        "title": "Abanet Link",
        "html": "<div class='min-h-screen bg-white dark:bg-gray-950 flex flex-col font-sans'><div class='w-full px-5 py-4 flex items-center justify-between bg-white dark:bg-gray-950 border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-900 sticky top-0 z-20'><div class='flex items-center gap-2.5'><div class='w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 overflow-hidden'><img src='{{global.logo}}' alt='' class='w-full h-full object-contain' onerror=\"this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'\" /><span style='display:none' class='w-full h-full bg-brand-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black text-xs'>AB</span></div><span class='font-black text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-sm uppercase tracking-tight'>{{global.company_name}}</span></div><a href='/login' class='px-4 py-2 bg-brand-500 hover:bg-brand-600 text-white rounded-xl text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest transition-all active:scale-95'>Login</a></div><div class='relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500 via-brand-600 to-blue-700 px-6 py-16 flex flex-col items-center text-center'><div class='absolute inset-0 opacity-10' style='background-image:radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%,white 1px,transparent 1px),radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%,white 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:40px 40px'></div><div class='relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-5 max-w-lg'><div class='inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/30 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5'><span class='w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 animate-pulse'></span><span class='text-white text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest'>Internet Rumah &amp; Bisnis</span></div><h1 class='text-4xl font-black text-white leading-tight tracking-tight'>Internet Cepat<br/><span class='text-yellow-300'>Harga Terjangkau</span></h1><p class='text-white/80 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-sm'>Koneksi stabil untuk streaming, gaming, WFH, dan semua kebutuhan online kamu bersama <strong class='text-white'>Abanet Link</strong>.</p><a href='#paket' class='px-8 py-3.5 bg-white text-brand-600 rounded-2xl font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest shadow-xl transition-all active:scale-95 hover:shadow-2xl'>Lihat Paket &darr;</a><p class='text-white/50 text-xs'>Sudah pelanggan? <a href='/login' class='text-white/80 underline underline-offset-2'>Login di sini</a></p></div></div><div class='px-5 py-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto w-full'><p class='text-xs font-bold text-brand-500 uppercase tracking-widest text-center mb-2'>Kenapa pilih kami?</p><h2 class='text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-center mb-8 tracking-tight'>Koneksi yang bisa kamu andalkan</h2><div class='grid grid-cols-1 gap-4'><div class='flex items-start gap-4 p-5 rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800'><div class='w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-blue-500/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0'><svg class='w-5 h-5 text-blue-500' fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2'><path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' d='M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z'/></svg></div><div><p class='font-black text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-sm'>Kecepatan Konsisten</p><p class='text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-xs mt-1 leading-relaxed'>Bandwidth dedicated, bukan shared. Tidak melambat di jam sibuk.</p></div></div><div class='flex items-start gap-4 p-5 rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800'><div class='w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0'><svg class='w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500' fill='none' viewBox='0 0 24 24' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2'><path stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round' d='M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z'/></svg></div><div><p cl